Text:
If (like I did) you didn't have any audio on the "South Park - S00E01 - The Spirit of Christmas (Jesus vs. Frosty).avi" file with an error code like this:

majortype: MEDIATYPE_Audio {73647561-0000-0010-8000-00AA00389B71}
subtype: Unknown GUID Name {34616D69-0000-0010-8000-00AA00389B71}

Open up the ffdshow audio decoder configuration then on the codecs list, locate "IMA ADPCM" and change the decoder from disabled to whatever codec is available to you (libavcodec perhaps).

Other than that, great torrent, thanks!
